o saw that the divine force permeates all matter, and that all matter there=
fore has a force of consciousness. The process of the divine spirit descend=
ing down into matter is called involution. The process by which the divine =
ascends back upwards out of matter is called evolution. According to Sri Au=
robindo, humanity has reached a stage where these two events are occurring =
simultaneously, and in his inner visions, he foresaw that we would soon be =
experiencing a descent of what he called =EF=BF=BDsupramental (or monadic) =
