t in what he makes possible. An immortal soul is somewhere within him, even=
 if seldom active in most people, while an eternal spirit overshadows him, =
even if obstructed from descent by the hard lid of his constructed personal=
ity. There is a great divine plan in motion, even if the evidence of the ou=
ter senses seems to contradict it.

