 is going through an evolutionary crisis. A stage has been reached in which=
 the human mind has made tremendous strides on the one hand, but is left ho=
pelessly inadequate to prevent its own extinction as a species. Meanwhile, =
as the Mother testified before her death in 1973, a consciousness higher th=
an the human rational mind, what may be termed the Supermind, has recently =
been established in the fields of the Earth, and is active there. Our task =
now is to bring it down into cellular consciousness.

